{"tid":1186653,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日81歲老人逆向行駛釀2死7傷事故","createTime":"2019-06-05T05:37:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-05T06:43:38.000Z","uid":32511,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b512284391565980f4e7549704d1e329f709eb96","tid":1186653,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T05:37:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nYL7mU4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnYL7mU4.jpg&h=b5842178&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本福岡市早良區4日晚間發生81歲老人開車逆向行駛，連續衝撞5輛車的事故，肇事的小島吉正及同車的76歲妻子送醫後不治死亡，被撞的車上乘客及路人共7人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n日媒報導，該老人駕駛小型廂型車於4日晚點7點過後，在早良區離十字路口約600公尺處先追撞前方車輛，再越過中央線衝進反向車道，加速逆向行駛，在連續撞了2部車後衝進交通流量大的十字路口，直到撞進大樓才停下來。<br />\n<br />\n有目擊者指出，肇事車當時的速度應該將近時速100公里左右，看不出來有踩煞車的跡象。<br />\n<br />\n這起交通事故造成兩部車被撞到人行道上，另有1部車翻覆、1部車前車窗被撞破裂。肇事者夫妻送醫急救後都不治死亡。被撞的包括男性路人在內的7名男女受傷。<br />\n<br />\n大阪此花區3日晚間才發生80歲的駕駛因方向盤操作錯誤撞上人行道的事故，造成4人輕傷。肇事者指出，倒車時油門和煞車踩錯了，才撞到人行道上。4月時東京池袋才發生87歲老人開車撞死母子的事故。<br />\n<br />\n日本高齡者危險駕駛的問題層出不窮，日本警察廳呼籲65歲以上老人主動退還駕照，不要再開車，以免傷人傷己。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zsxhysTY7vg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzsxhysTY7vg&d=bqe6r6CGoyJNILHzVVCKL5hbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=72225398\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zsxhysTY7vg</a>"},{"pid":"4a9d5605fff48f3d9fea217db01a33305a9b1cc9","tid":1186653,"uid":18251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T05:43:00.000Z","msg":"老人會不會是外來物種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87052a5e046720105493319c13f4fad1b1588ead","tid":1186653,"uid":117927,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T05:45:40.000Z","msg":"老害 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d812f26687f6620813266e4c87c8dce8168667f1","tid":1186653,"uid":44646,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T05:47:44.000Z","msg":"強伯開車去探朋友<br />\n一路開車一路聽收音機，節目主持話有特別馬路消息：<br />\n「駕駛人士留意，XX公路有一架私家車逆向行駛」<br />\n<br />\n強伯聽到屌出聲<br />\n「仆街啦，明明幾百架車逆向行駛！」"},{"pid":"c334291cede97e4d71f7bde75490c45b9b4ac6d2","tid":1186653,"uid":239321,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T05:47:56.000Z","msg":"屌，已經係近期既第三單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞到我呢排都唔敢開車"},{"pid":"0d0f862f15e2e611e7b99445287b852ddb8f7a73","tid":1186653,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T05:49:39.000Z","msg":"阿伯想自殺？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6bd79d84cff96cc5bbdc9f295969d16643d0cb1","tid":1186653,"uid":470,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T05:51:16.000Z","msg":"好彩死嘅係佢地自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1fa0e7c66dd77a61d26fddd962f71152f1bf0c1","tid":1186653,"uid":191815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T06:29:41.000Z","msg":"日本好多老人駕駛<br />\n去到鄉郊地方更普遍，人口老化，人口唔集中，公共交通\b都做唔住，迫住一定要揸。"},{"pid":"95d11b9bde8ee96f595618ef580c52a2d1aa38ac","tid":1186653,"uid":56453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d812f26687f6620813266e4c87c8dce8168667f1","tid":1186653,"uid":44646,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T05:47:44.000Z","msg":"強伯開車去探朋友<br />\n一路開車一路聽收音機，節目主持話有特別馬路消息：<br />\n「駕駛人士留意，XX公路有一架私家車逆向行駛」<br />\n<br />\n強伯聽到屌出聲<br />\n「仆街啦，明明幾百架車逆向行駛！」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T06:30:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e593832d740b5fa7ee756ae4b07c142662da7ee3","tid":1186653,"uid":253413,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T06:31:03.000Z","msg":"日本人最怕帶麻煩畀人同冇面子，老人家今次咁錯，隨時要自殺謝罪"},{"pid":"48f010209a88e13360efea15c68247de07e0e54c","tid":1186653,"uid":50041,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e593832d740b5fa7ee756ae4b07c142662da7ee3","tid":1186653,"uid":253413,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T06:31:03.000Z","msg":"日本人最怕帶麻煩畀人同冇面子，老人家今次咁錯，隨時要自殺謝罪"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T06:31:47.000Z","msg":"死左啦"},{"pid":"d01b41c476e96a7d283e5baa5f82d32aa883ab1b","tid":1186653,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T06:32:48.000Z","msg":"廢老？"},{"pid":"ba13fed576bfafda6d6c76b87f974cc5c6e772c9","tid":1186653,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T06:43:38.000Z","msg":"日本老人家因為自尊心，加上泡沫經濟時代既影響，輝煌慣、嘆慣，老左打死都唔願交個牌出黎<br />\n<br />\n而且對日本老人黎講，出行冇想像既方便"}]}